plot: Elke and Annette Döring see in the news that both Elke and Lilo Gottschick are being sought by the police. Tina meets Patrick's father, who shows his best side. The old Löpelmann is furious when he learns of Tina's contacts with the old earl. He wants to kick her out. When Annette leaves Elke alone for a few minutes, Lilo Gottschick appears. She pushes the girl into a corner of the room and chokes her. But Annette is back faster than expected and intervenes.
